Fuel Consumption - Nanocomposite Test Results - Review by Alexander Michelson
07 Nov 2019 by Alexander Michelson
Reduce fuel consumption! This is the third video from the Amortect PROOF nanocomposite test series. Perhaps the most interesting is the final review. In this case, the results obtained by PEOPLE TESTERS, to whom we sent the additive completely free. A total of 15 sets were sent, but unfortunately not all volunteers received the packages ... However, those who reported on their impressions are quite enough to draw conclusions about the effectiveness of the additive. So, how to reduce gas mileage and does Amortect PROOF help?
